OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F423A1777576265
OL,3,CMan, 80, jailed for violence against
OL,4,Cwomen dating back to 1990s
OL,6,FAn 80-year-old man has been jailed for
OL,7,Fviolence against women dating back to
OL,8,Fthe 1990s.
OL,10,FVincent Agar, formerly from
OL,11,FMiddlesbrough, was extradited from
OL,12,FThailand last year to face justice
OL,13,Ffollowing a six-year investigation by
OL,14,Fpolice.
OL,16,FHe was jailed for 19 years at Durham
OL,17,FCrown Court on Thursday, Cleveland
OL,18,FPolice said.
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G1/6
