OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F423A1777576265
OL,3,CMan, 80, jailed for violence against
OL,4,Cwomen dating back to 1990s
OL,6,FAgar's involvement in historical
OL,7,Fviolence was highlighted to officers
OL,8,Finvestigating the murders of three
OL,9,Fyoung women from the Teesside area,
OL,10,Funder Operation Pandect.
OL,12,FThey interviewed dozens of women who
OL,13,Fwere potential witnesses and two of
OL,14,Fthem came forward to say Agar had
OL,15,Fsubjected them to extreme violence and
OL,16,Fimprisoned them within his house.
OL,18,FOne victim was threatened and held
OL,19,Fagainst her will after she saw another
OL,20,Fwoman tied to a radiator at his flat.
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G2/6
OL,2,W/*%+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,
