FL,424,420,120,260,000,100
PN,42303
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F423A1777576265
OL,3,CMan, 80, jailed for violence against
OL,4,Cwomen dating back to 1990s
OL,6,FIn separate incidents between 1998 and
OL,7,F2000, they were subjected to extreme
OL,8,Fviolence which included being cut with
OL,9,Fknives, assaulted with a belt, hammer
OL,10,Fand bottle and being burnt with a
OL,11,Fkettle, iron and cigarettes.
OL,13,FThey managed to escape the drug
OL,14,Fdealer's flat, which was heavily
OL,15,Fsecured.
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G3/6
OL,2,W/*%+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,
