FL,424,420,120,260,000,100
PN,42304
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F423A1777576265
OL,3,CMan, 80, jailed for violence against
OL,4,Cwomen dating back to 1990s
OL,6,FAgar was found to be living on the
OL,7,FThai island of Koh Samui and was
OL,8,Feventually extradited and charged with
OL,9,Fa series of offences, including
OL,10,Fgrievous bodily harm with intent,
OL,11,Ffalse imprisonment, actual bodily
OL,12,Fharm, threats to kill and supplying a
OL,13,Fclass A drug.
OL,15,FHe denied the charges but was
OL,16,Fconvicted following a trial.
OL,18,FIn a victim impact statement, one
OL,19,Fwoman said she will be affected for
OL,20,Fthe rest of her life.
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G4/6
