CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F423A1777576265
OL,3,CMan, 80, jailed for violence against
OL,4,Cwomen dating back to 1990s
OL,6,FJudge Richard Bennett told Agar: "Your
OL,7,Foffending has now caught up with you."
OL,9,FOutside court, senior investigating
OL,10,Fofficer Detective Superintendent Peter
OL,11,FCarr said: "This case is a
OL,12,Fdemonstration that no matter how long
OL,13,Fthe passage of time, we will take
OL,14,Faction against those who commit such
OL,15,Fhorrendous criminal offences and we
OL,16,Fwill not tolerate violence against
OL,17,Fwomen and girls."
